    <!--
    PLEASE NOTE: Since adding transparency to already
    defined colors is not supported through xml, we have
    to add them manually. This means: we have used blue_grey
    color scheme, and this is where we use blue_grey500 color
    to add transparency. If you were about to change color
    scheme, also change blue_grey500 color from here. Below 
    you have 5 different themes that we provide for you. You
    just need to uncomment some theme, and comment "Blue Grey"
    and that is it. If you like to change by yourself in some
    different theme you can do that easily. We have 4 colors
    related to theme: primary, secondary, tertiary and text color. 
    If you want to change all colors in same, please change where 
    you see primary, secondary and tertary. We provide for you
    opportunity to change different parts in app. You can see
    below that we sepparate: action bar color, action bar text
    color, left menu color and color of background in full screen
    image. If few clicks, you can customize all colors in whole app.
    So, you have possibility to change all colors in one place
    (main_color_primary, main_color_secondary or main_color_tertary),
    or you have possibility to separate colors of action_bar_color,
    action_bar_text_color, left_menu_color and full_screen_image_background.
    That is your choice, do you want to all colors be related, or
    you want separate some elements from main color. :)
    
    -->


